<paragraph id="982D1956299ABF81333CA9C3C7585D35" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Krainer Wolfsmilch</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
</title>
<subSubSection id="56611E7846D9CBAE76D6D99B2BAC64E6" pageId="null" pageNumber="664" type="description">
<paragraph id="06B2D301EFF0D19706ED6111DA0AF34E" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="DA701DC23D72D4DAA5F9A76B957C98FB" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="664" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="verrucosa">
<emphasis id="C7BC574FDBCC5A843F32C147E453F44B" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">E. verrucosa</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 12) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="2CCBFB09ABCDAF02C9723C95BCDE5EEB" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
<normalizedToken id="7240807DC877D0573491E04B8920C7AD" originalValue="Blätter" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Blaetter</normalizedToken>
nicht 
<normalizedToken id="ED46A1701BCEDCC1C29048534CCC2A00" originalValue="gezähnt" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">gezaehnt</normalizedToken>
;
</emphasis>
Stiele 1. Ordnung des 
<normalizedToken id="ED49BB3C698FFA454D1914790A342C9B" originalValue="Gesamtblütenstandes" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Gesamtbluetenstandes</normalizedToken>
mindestens 1mal gabelig geteilt, 
<normalizedToken id="B48E6C6DDC1F07D9BF1BB74FBBF1513C" originalValue="Gesamtblütenstand" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Gesamtbluetenstand</normalizedToken>
deshalb 
<normalizedToken id="15FB09A8AD250D0F798FD05E5A74C773" originalValue="größer" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">groesser</normalizedToken>
. Samen 3,2-3,7 mm lang, 2,7-2,9 mm dick, 
<emphasis id="95CB07587877498371B6630F6DC164EC" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">glatt</emphasis>
, braun bis grau. - 
<normalizedToken id="3612FFAD2577F975964B2A1E9D097DA4" originalValue="Blüte" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Bluete</normalizedToken>
: 
<normalizedToken id="8B348EDE17F661417082BD9086E45704" originalValue="Frühling" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Fruehling</normalizedToken>
und 
<normalizedToken id="4FCED9CB873275AA04D33F77EE55B8CB" originalValue="früher" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">frueher</normalizedToken>
Sommer.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7299355A6E99832FAEE5C9F9F1F3AF3E" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
<emphasis id="845A0F4089518ACA131BE76B93BBEA13" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Zytologische Angaben.</emphasis>
Keine Untersuchungen.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="7EE1EB0B2EC0A6E34790F378518D43FC" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
<emphasis id="19A20093B38CAF5505896292EF3CE6D9" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Standort.</emphasis>
Kollin und montan. Wie 
<taxonomicName id="437BCB3727C87FC60BB29343DCBC30EC" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Euphorbiaceae" genus="Euphorbia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Malpighiales" pageId="null" pageNumber="664" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="dulcis">
<emphasis id="E49DA386E85BB7B2D8A0FB06D3E6F796" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">E. dulcis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(Nr. 10). 
<normalizedToken id="BEC24F307EB887F68C6836BC62B40478" originalValue="Buchenwälder" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Buchenwaelder</normalizedToken>
.
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="1D0E4D6DB78F25AE0F65C4FD181DB20A" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
<emphasis id="08588835AE02C6B09355F6BAF2D95CF0" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">
Verbreitung. 
<normalizedToken id="DFB4FCE5C67EA008237CF10482AFF7AE" originalValue="Südeuropäische" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Suedeuropaeische</normalizedToken>
Gebirgspflanze (
<normalizedToken id="8872E14239593B323F7970F1E62B6E7F" originalValue="östlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">oestlich</normalizedToken>
):
</emphasis>
<normalizedToken id="E3F7C3EFDAC09AF76BED60DA6FC7B168" originalValue="Westwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Westwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Piemont (Biella), durch die 
<normalizedToken id="DD1B29BD429E152E3B33348746F92ADE" originalValue="südlichen" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">suedlichen</normalizedToken>
Kalkalpen 
<normalizedToken id="29FE337754887AC18FAB6FF3CAA62182" originalValue="ostwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">ostwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Steiermark, Euganeen, illyrische Gebirge, Donaubecken (
<normalizedToken id="D269EA0A6CDA23BCC07FB2C4D3EA03D5" originalValue="nordwärts" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">nordwaerts</normalizedToken>
bis Moldau), 
<normalizedToken id="A642E9332586B947D8C4209F393EE4EA" originalValue="Südkarpaten" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">Suedkarpaten</normalizedToken>
. Verbreitungskarte von Meusel (1955-1956). - Im Gebiet: Piemont (
<normalizedToken id="12A34302BA5023CB606504EF1B618173" originalValue="nördlich" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">noerdlich</normalizedToken>
Biella [Valsessera], Valsesia [Civiasco]), Tessin (Tenero bei Locarno), Comerseegebiet (Corni di Canzo, Grigna, Resegone, Carenno), Bergamasker Alpen (Selvino, Oneta, Lago 
<normalizedToken id="2F8EA0F09167D7A3FD4B1ED49699FCAF" originalValue="d’Iseo" pageId="null" pageNumber="664">d'Iseo</normalizedToken>
), Meran, Unterengadin (Vulpera, Tarasp).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
